79
00:07:00,136 --> 00:07:04,368
Yes, I must say, you don't look a day
over 20. No. Oh, yes.

80
00:07:05,441 --> 00:07:08,171
Smile, darling, smile.

81
00:07:12,748 --> 00:07:17,310
Well, hello. What a pleasure.
Welcome to our home.

82
00:07:17,854 --> 00:07:19,082
Thank you.

83
00:07:19,255 --> 00:07:22,588
We'll be taking tea
in the west drawing room.

84
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:26,620
Oh, do come this way,
it's just through there.

85
00:07:26,796 --> 00:07:31,028
Oh, I love what you've done with the place.
Who is your decorator?

86
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,225
Nice tiles, shame about the drapes.

87
00:07:33,402 --> 00:07:36,894
