Ignore him.

88
00:07:37,406 --> 00:07:39,499
Yes, it's usually best.

89
00:09:07,930 --> 00:09:11,491
- Do forgive me.
- You play beautifully.

90
00:09:11,667 --> 00:09:16,934
I... I... I do apologize, Miss Everglot.
How rude of me to... Well...

91
